Class JModeMirrorPanel

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container

                  de.iabg.mode.JModeMirrorPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Loggable, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class JModeMirrorPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements Loggable

An implementation for a JPanel containing two JModePanel objects with the First Mode panel placed vertically above the Last Model panel. This is simply a convenience class to instantiate the two JModePanel components and provides no other additional functionality. This component is also Loggable and simply relays or chains any LogEvents from the First Mode panel or the Last Mode panel.

Version:
September 12, 2008
Author:
